  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[On Play] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Add 1 Digimon
    card with [Vegetation], [Plant] or [Fairy] in one of its traits among them to
    the hand. Return the rest to the bottom of the deck. [Your Turn] When an effect
    suspends a Digimon, by suspending this Tamer, gain 1 memory.'
